Usage:
    difflicious --help
    difflicious [--interactive] [--json] [--plain] [--report-directory <directory>]... [--test-id <ulid>] [--no-color]

View Difflicious JSON diffs interactively, as JSON, or as plain text.

Options and flags:
    --help, -h
        Display this help text.
    --interactive
        Open the interactive terminal viewer.
    --json
        Print machine-readable JSON.
    --plain
        Print a plain-text summary.
    --report-directory <directory>, -d <directory>
        Directory containing Difflicious JSONL reports. May be specified multiple times.
    --test-id <ulid>
        Show only the matching reporter ULID in non-interactive modes, or jump to it in TUI mode.
    --no-color
        Disable ANSI color in TUI output.
